@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam usecaseFontSize 10

left to right direction

actor "Project Lead" as PL

usecase "Xóa dự án" as UC_Delete
usecase "Xác nhận\nbằng identifier" as UC_Confirm
usecase "Kiểm tra\nquyền" as UC_CheckPerm
usecase "Cascade delete\ntất cả dữ liệu" as UC_Cascade

PL --> UC_Delete

UC_Confirm .up.> UC_Delete : <<include>>
UC_CheckPerm .up.> UC_Delete : <<include>>
UC_Cascade .up.> UC_Delete : <<include>>

note right of UC_Confirm
  User phải nhập đúng
  identifier để xác nhận
end note

note bottom of UC_Cascade
  Xóa toàn bộ:
  • Sprints
  • Issues
  • Issue Statuses
  • Comments
  • Activities
end note

note left of UC_CheckPerm
  Chỉ Project Lead
  mới có quyền xóa
end note

@enduml
